a tape file merge pattern generator.wa routine is presented which specifies thesequence of merge cycles to effect the merging of sorted tape files.  the routine is designed to minimizeelapsed computer time by varying the power of the merge cycles, so as to use all the available tapedrives, with its characteristic of assigning one drive to a single-reel file and two drives to each multiple-reel file.cacm may, cooke, w. s.ca jb march ,   : am